text: Henry Thompson (born 1 December 1992) is an English cricketer. He is a right- handed batsman and a right-arm off break bowler. He made his first-class debut for Leeds/Bradford MCCU against Yorkshire on 5 April 2013. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1992 births Category:Living people Category:English cricketers Category:Leeds/Bradford MCCU cricketers Category:Sportspeople from Preston, Lancashire
